name: Sensser
overview:
Sensser is an early stage technology start-up founded in Melbourne, Australia

The Sensser application is a new and improved, real-time phonebook which aims to make communicating with one another a lot easier. It has been released on iPhone, with the intention of developing for other platforms including Android, RIM and Windows.

As phones became smarter, phone books and contact cards stayed the same. Native phone books are static, boring and lack the information, updates and content that smart-phone users need to stay in touch. Sensser aims to be your smart phone book, making every day phone calls, communication and contact management a little bit easier.
